@page "/"
@inject IStringLocalizer<App> Localize

<div class="page-container">

    <div class="mat-layout-grid">
        <div class="mat-layout-grid-inner">
            <div class="mat-layout-grid-cell main-text mat-layout-grid-cell-span-12">
                <img class="main-image" src="http://miamidsa.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Fund-the-People-Miami.jpg" />
                <p>
                    @Localize["Every July, Miami-Dade County releases its plan for how to spend our money in our communities for the next year. The July release is meant to give County residents time to review the budget and make comments before it is adopted in September. The"]
                    <a href="https://www.miamidade.gov/global/management/budget/2020-21-proposed-budget.page" target=”_blank”>
                        @Localize["Proposed Budget"]
                    </a>
                    @Localize[", however, is a mammoth document with hundreds of pages of text, tables, and graphs spread across three volumes and two dozen appendices."]
                </p>
                <p>
                    @Localize["Fundthepeoplemiami.com is our attempt to break down this mammoth document. We undertook this work with a group of community organizations in the wake of George Floyd’s death, and it soon became apparent that the disproportionate amount of spending on local law enforcement being decried across the country was also evident in Miami. In this first iteration of the website, we focus on the discrepancies between our county’s funding for policing versus non-violent social services. We hope that as more people join our efforts and new findings are made we can create the most powerful and accessible budget visualization tool our communities deserve."]
                </p>

                <MatHeadline6 Style="color: green; font-weight: 700;">
                    @Localize["HOW WE CHANGE THE BUDGET"]
                </MatHeadline6>

                <p>
                    @Localize[@"Our chance to tell County Commissioners how we want our money spent is taking place digitally this Thursday, September 3rd at 5:00pm via Zoom."]
                    <a href="https://www.miamidade.gov/commission/registration/2020-09-03-BCC-meeting-registration.asp">
                        @Localize["Click here to register and make a public comment!"]
                    </a>
                </p>

                <p>
                    @Localize["You also reach out to your County Commissioner directly before September 19th’s final vote!"]
                    <a href="/Resources">
                        @Localize["Visit our Resources page"]
                    </a>
                    @Localize["to find your district and the commissioner’s contact information!"]
                </p>

                <MatHeadline6 Style="color: #B89413;font-weight: 700;">
                    @Localize["SPECIAL THANKS"]
                </MatHeadline6>

                <p>
                    @Localize["The research, illustrations and design presented here is the accumulated work of many individuals—workers, students and everyday citizens who are dedicated to seeing economic justice and real democracy here in Miami. Without them and the organizations they are a part of this website and the information it makes available to our communities would not have been possible."]
                </p>



            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

